---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl space-y-8 px-4 py-16 text-center sm:space-y-10 sm:py-28">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold font-heading text-text sm:text-5xl">お問い合わせ</h1>
    <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text/80 sm:text-lg">
      swimmin&apos; parade への出演や取材に関するご連絡は
      X（旧Twitter）のダイレクトメッセージで受け付けています。
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://x.com/swipara2023?s=21"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex w-full max-w-[320px] items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent px-10 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-pop transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-primary"
      aria-label="Swimmin' Parade の X (Twitter) アカウントへ移動する"
    >
      X（Twitter）で連絡する
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>
